Foot-and-mouth disease [FMD] - Mongolia
---------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 25 Jul 2016 from Dr Battsengel Dambadarjaa, Chief Veterinary Officer Director, Veterinary and Animal Breeding Service, Ministry for Food and Agriculture, Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 16 Jul 2016
Date of confirmation of the event: 22 Jul 2016
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 23 Nov 2015
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: food and mouth disease virus
Serotype: A
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains a defined zone within the country.

